<parameterdescription>
<para>graph that will contain the skeleton of <computeroutput>tmesh</computeroutput>. For each vertex descriptor <computeroutput>vd</computeroutput> of <computeroutput>skeleton</computeroutput>, the corresponding point and the set of input vertices that contracted to <computeroutput>vd</computeroutput> can be retrieved using <computeroutput>skeleton[vd].point</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>skeleton[vd].vertices</computeroutput> respectively. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
